title: Defense Combine Preview
itunes:title: Defense Combine Preview
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks are back with a new episode. To start off, the guys talk about the top defensive tackle prospects that will be at the combine (1:15). Then, the pair previews the best edge rushers to watch out for (13:33). After, the duo looks at the linebackers they’re looking forward to seeing (29:23). Next, the guys discuss what to expect from the top cornerbacks (38:27) and to wrap up the show, the pair analyze the safety prospects at the combine (45:46).

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
